body:
I've been looking through Youtube looking for smaller channels to make a collab video with but haven't had much luck. So here I am. If there is anyone looking to duo or collab with me I'm in. 

The link to my channel is here so you guys can check it out if you want. 

Thanks for taking the time to read this!
